    "text_with_icons_mN4rNg": {
      "type": "text-with-icons",
      "blocks": {
        "item_xJRqeR": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-coupon",
            "custom_icon": "shopify://shop_images/doddl_2023_Engineered_Icon_7316c180-cca0-4c4b-bc9e-477fcb1c0f44.png",
            "mobile_icon_width": 120,
            "icon_width": 120,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#343a40",
            "title": "Short chunky handles",
            "content": "<p>The unique design of doddl cutlery makes it easier for children with reduced grip, hand or arm function, sensory and fine motor difficulties to eat successfully. <strong>Short, chunky handles </strong>are much easier to control whilst helping your child develop a stronger grip and better co-ordination. </p>"
          }
        },
        "item_QET6HB": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-coupon",
            "custom_icon": "shopify://shop_images/doddl_2023_5_Star_Reviews_Icon_87e17495-9c36-47c3-818c-9523553b5ed0.png",
            "mobile_icon_width": 120,
            "icon_width": 120,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#301562",
            "title": "Easy grip design",
            "content": "<p>Soft touch areas encourage correct finger placement and makes the <strong>cutlery handles easier to grip</strong>. The handle of the doddl knife sits comfortably in your child’s palm allowing them to push down through all types of food successfully. doddl has been thoughtfully designed alongside development experts who both <strong>approve and recommend</strong> doddl.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_c7ARnn": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-coupon",
            "custom_icon": "shopify://shop_images/doddl_2023_Certified_safe_Icon_f747756e-fe6d-4d2f-8bc9-cb42a7684b83.png",
            "mobile_icon_width": 120,
            "icon_width": 120,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#301562",
            "title": "Engineered for success",
            "content": "<p>The doddl knife, fork and spoon are certified safe but are highly effective, enabling successful scooping, stabbing, and chopping of all food, <strong>helping to build confidence </strong>and independence in every child. High quality and incredibly long lasting doddl can be used between 12 months and 5+ years and beyond.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
